    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is cooking, add a handful of <strong>flour</strong> to a plate with the <strong>remaining dried oregano </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your <strong>herby flour</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper and add to the <strong>herby flour</strong>, turn several times until fully coated<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>coated hake</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1690285539269-x200.jpg",
