    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic </strong>with your <strong>mayo </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
