      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>to a large bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Once the croutons and roasted veg are cooked, add them to the dressing with the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong></p><p>Crumble in your <strong>feta </strong>and gently toss it all together – this is your <strong>roasted Greek-style salad</strong></p>",
