      "instruction": "<p>Serve your <strong>pan-fried hake </strong>with the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and <strong>roasted Greek-style salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>over the hake and potatoes</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
